globs:
  - "**/*.py"  # Apply to all Python files
  - "**/*.pyi" # Apply to Python stub files
alwaysApply: true
---

Avoid hardcoding configuration values (like API keys, database URLs, file paths) directly in the code. Suggest using environment variables, configuration files (e.g., YAML, TOML, .env), or dedicated configuration management libraries.

